---
title: Smart Louisiana Sunburst Salad with Cajun Turkey
description: Made famous by the Palace Café in New Orleans, this dish brings a whole new spin on the classic 'mixed greens' style salad. Sweet, spicy, tart and topped with Cajun-spiced turkey. You'll swear you were in the French Quarter!

